{"title":"Unit 1 Faro smart helmet boasts automatic brake lights, remote-operated turn signals, more!","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/11/09/unit-1-faro-smart-helmet-boasts-automatic-brake-lights-remote-operated-turn-signals-more/","date":1636471930000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09102249/unit-1-faro-grey-commuter-helmet-with-LEDa-1.jpg\" data-fancybox=\"\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09102249/unit-1-faro-grey-commuter-helmet-with-LEDa-1-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09102249/unit-1-faro-grey-commuter-helmet-with-LEDa-1-800x534.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09102249/unit-1-faro-grey-commuter-helmet-with-LEDa-1-297x198.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09102249/unit-1-faro-grey-commuter-helmet-with-LEDa-1-120x80.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09102249/unit-1-faro-grey-commuter-helmet-with-LEDa-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09102249/unit-1-faro-grey-commuter-helmet-with-LEDa-1-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09102249/unit-1-faro-grey-commuter-helmet-with-LEDa-1.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></a><header></header><p>Support us! BikeRumor may earn a small commission from affiliate links in this article. <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/privacy\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a>.</p></div><div role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-277923\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>Unit 1 has released what could very well be the ultimate helmet for urban cycle commuters. Integrated into its sleek veneer is a host of LEDs at the rear that serve to inform traffic of the rider’s intentions. Braking? The Faro has automatic lights for that. Turning left or right? Use the handlebar-mounted remote to send moving arrows across the back of the helmet, clearly indicating the direction you’re about to turn. This helmet is packed to the brim with cool safety features… here’s more.</p><p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/IpuNrQk-c9M?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en-US&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation\"></iframe></p><h2>Unit 1 Faro Helmet</h2><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101835/unit-1-faro-black-smart-commuter-helmet-led-braking-lights.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101835/unit-1-faro-black-smart-commuter-helmet-led-braking-lights.jpg\" alt=\"unit 1 faro smart commuter helmet automatic brake lights remote operated turn signals crash detector mips\" width=\"1600\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101835/unit-1-faro-black-smart-commuter-helmet-led-braking-lights.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101835/unit-1-faro-black-smart-commuter-helmet-led-braking-lights-297x167.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101835/unit-1-faro-black-smart-commuter-helmet-led-braking-lights-800x450.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101835/unit-1-faro-black-smart-commuter-helmet-led-braking-lights-120x68.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101835/unit-1-faro-black-smart-commuter-helmet-led-braking-lights-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101835/unit-1-faro-black-smart-commuter-helmet-led-braking-lights-1536x864.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p>In addition to its strip of white LEDs out front, and red LEDs on the rear, the Unit 1 Faro Smart Helmet packs a further 40 LEDs at the rear, the behavior and color of which is customizable through the Faro App. An accelerometer inside the shell detects when the rider is slowing down triggering the LEDs to light up indicating to traffic that you’re braking.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101847/unit-1-faro-indicator-brake-light.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101847/unit-1-faro-indicator-brake-light.jpg\" alt=\"unit 1 faro brake indicator turn signal leds\" width=\"1600\" height=\"589\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101847/unit-1-faro-indicator-brake-light.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101847/unit-1-faro-indicator-brake-light-297x109.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101847/unit-1-faro-indicator-brake-light-800x295.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101847/unit-1-faro-indicator-brake-light-120x44.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101847/unit-1-faro-indicator-brake-light-768x283.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101847/unit-1-faro-indicator-brake-light-1536x565.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p>It seems you can tune that too; you can have them flash quickly to be more attention-grabbing than to just simply stay on continuously through the braking. That accelerometer serves another purpose; that of a crash detector. If it senses the helmet come to a very sudden stop, it communicates with the Faro App on your smartphone to alert your chosen emergency contacts of a fall.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101923/unit-1-faor-handlebar-remote-indicator.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101923/unit-1-faor-handlebar-remote-indicator.jpg\" alt=\"unit 1 faro handlebar mounted turn signal remote\" width=\"1600\" height=\"861\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101923/unit-1-faor-handlebar-remote-indicator.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101923/unit-1-faor-handlebar-remote-indicator-297x160.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101923/unit-1-faor-handlebar-remote-indicator-800x431.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101923/unit-1-faor-handlebar-remote-indicator-120x65.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101923/unit-1-faor-handlebar-remote-indicator-768x413.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101923/unit-1-faor-handlebar-remote-indicator-1536x827.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p>The handlebar-mounted remote is an optional add-on. Simple left and right buttons allow you to indicate at junctions to let traffic at the rear and side know that you’re making a turn – without taking your hands off the grips. The lights for that can be customized too; choose flashing arrows that move in the direction you’re turning, or opt for a block of lights to flash on either side, a bit more like the indicators on cars.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101926/unit-1-faor-mips-commuter-helmet-leds-smart.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101926/unit-1-faor-mips-commuter-helmet-leds-smart.jpg\" alt=\"unit 1 faro mips add on\" width=\"1600\" height=\"984\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101926/unit-1-faor-mips-commuter-helmet-leds-smart.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101926/unit-1-faor-mips-commuter-helmet-leds-smart-297x183.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101926/unit-1-faor-mips-commuter-helmet-leds-smart-800x492.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101926/unit-1-faor-mips-commuter-helmet-leds-smart-120x74.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101926/unit-1-faor-mips-commuter-helmet-leds-smart-768x472.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101926/unit-1-faor-mips-commuter-helmet-leds-smart-1536x945.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><p>MIPS is another optional add-on. This is a separate liner that sits inside the EPS liner that allows the helmet to rotate 10-15mm in any direction upon impact <em>independently</em> to the wearer’s head, reducing energy transferred to the rider. It’s a common helmet safety technology used widely on performance road and mountain bike helmets and is said to make any helmet around 10% safer.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101850/unit-1-faro-smart-helmet-app-2.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101850/unit-1-faro-smart-helmet-app-2.jpg\" alt=\"unit 1 faro app customization\" width=\"1600\" height=\"791\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101850/unit-1-faro-smart-helmet-app-2.jpg 1600w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101850/unit-1-faro-smart-helmet-app-2-297x147.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101850/unit-1-faro-smart-helmet-app-2-800x396.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101850/unit-1-faro-smart-helmet-app-2-120x59.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101850/unit-1-faro-smart-helmet-app-2-768x380.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/09101850/unit-1-faro-smart-helmet-app-2-1536x759.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\"></a></p><h3>Pricing &amp; Availability</h3><p>The Unit 1 Faro Smart Helmet is available to pre-order direct from Unit 1 now, with a pre-order discount of 10% bringing the price down to £139.99. Add MIPS and a handlebar-mounted remote for an extra £26.47 each. The next batch is due to ship in late November.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.unit1gear.com/urban\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>Unit1Gear.com</em></a></p></section></article></div></div>","author":"Jessie-May Morgan","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"e9b8edddc78f797ce4b7324ad2b1cd4156a1d43b786cb4b8267ec35083f3f3cc","category":"Cycling"}